---
import ExperienceIcon from "../icons/ExperienceIcon.astro"
---

<section class="w-full h-auto grid place-content-center py-16 sm:py-4">
  <article
    class="min-w-xl h-8 flex justify-start items-center gap-x-4 mt-16 sm:mt-4 md:mt-8"
  >
    <div class="w-auto h-8">
      <ExperienceIcon />
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Experience</h2>
  </article>

  <article class="max-w-xl mt-4 ml-3">
    <ol class="relative border-s border-gray-20 w-full">
      <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
        <div
          class="absolute w-3 h-3 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white"
        >
        </div>
        <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400"
          >March 2022</time
        >
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          Junior Full-stack Developer in Quantum Outsourcing Group
        </h3>
        <ul class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span
              >Using the API of ChatGPT, I created a chatbot that helped to
              centralize all the important processes of the company instead of
              having multiple PDFs, Excels, etc.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span
              >Creating a clock-in tool that allows workers to generate their
              timesheets.</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span>I don't know what to put here</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>

      <li class="mb-10 ms-4">
        <div
          class="absolute w-3 h-3 rounded-full mt-1.5 -start-1.5 border border-white"
        >
        </div>
        <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400"
          >March 2021</time
        >
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">
          RPA Developer in Konecta
        </h3>
        <h4 class="font-semibold">Tasks</h4>

        <ul class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 space-y-1">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span
              >Talking to the operation (call center), and with the managers to
              develop the automation</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span
              >Improving between 20 to 30% the differents process of the
              operation which means getting more work done</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span
              >Helping the Company to save money on hiring due to the
              optimization in time, avoiding human mistakes</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-black mr-2">•</span>
            <span
              >I proposed and crafted a "magazine" where we can see the projects
              (UI, code and good practices), of the co-workers. This helped to
              improve our code and team-work</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </article>
</section>
